Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.60,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\frz270\shad2\pos(530,360)\4c&HF3EFF3&}Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來為名乃開一個生日會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不錯啊 什麼時候啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就今天！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 那種事情要事前通知一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒準備啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然今天不是名乃的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問問她麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要給她來個驚喜！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士的生日會也一起辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是一石二鳥啊 辦吧辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟讓人快樂的驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論準備的一方或接受的一方都會很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那回去的時候 大家一起買個蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣也覺得這樣OK麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘帶小錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒… 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就 小祐和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘帶錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前在遊樂園弄丟了你的錢也還沒還你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之今天我就先把錢出了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我現在去告訴名乃今天要辦生日會！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驚喜被你扔哪去了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小祐可真是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明… 明明被{笹原前輩甩了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才…！ 才沒被甩哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明邊哭邊跑來著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說 只是挽著胳膊也不知道有沒有在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說也還沒跟本人確認過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以完全就沒有被甩！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以完全不會放棄什麼的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還完全喜歡他呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些事情 多多拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有落下東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 那我就走了～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎… 怎麼回事啊 博士！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才啊 我做了一個小東西所以給你摘下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 「小東西」是什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「小東西」就是啊… 那個哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}那個… 那… 個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 後背就什麼都沒有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要從那個小東西上面…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 名乃？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大早晨的你們在幹什麼啊 這麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你又弄了什麼陷阱？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本吧小東西弄壞了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本把名乃弄哭了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪也該怪你亂丟東西吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 你忘了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還會馬上再做一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來之前能做好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我馬上就做嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士！ 我去上學了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.21,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs75\shad2\4c&HDFE6EB&\pos(750,360)}校\N長\N與\N教\N導\N主\N任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主任！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前 我還坐在校長寶座時候的銅像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要是 沒有東雲校長的像就奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 現在的年輕人的惡作劇是該說有幽默感呢還是愛胡鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是有支持者的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教導主任！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們搬完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這尊像放在這裡就可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主任… 這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真… 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的年輕人的惡作劇該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是夠精巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這尊像也請搬走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個粗製濫造的也要收拾走麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粗製濫造…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 這個土了吧唧的也拿走了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土了吧唧…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小氣的也要搬走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 教導主任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫生氣莫生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就跟剛才那個臭烘烘的一起拿走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丫說啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.68,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs75\shad2\4c&HDFE6EB&\pos(750,360)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs30\c&H221E1C&\pos(1083,376)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒上鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 關口你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想著我要第一個來 還開著黑鳥來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(882,654)}Black Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}黑鳥：美國開發的超音速偵察機SR-71的愛稱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 關口你也來晨練麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然你們倆的午飯都要我來買啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 沒有錢包的話也沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是美緒 度量大啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒… 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小祐你太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呦呦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問沒問名乃今天可不可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘記了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就稍微跟她說一聲要給她過生日！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那樣不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只問她今天可不可以去就夠了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才沒明白啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 麻衣麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moment please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just moment please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我稍微去找一下名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好事不宜遲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非… 非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沖吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太對不起啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然選黑咖啡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.55,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\frz9\pos(563,35)\c&H0B3259&}恭喜中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.55,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\frz9\pos(592,73)\c&H323963&}再來{\c&H4E40E5&}一{\c&H323963&}瓶{\c&H4E40E5&}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H523BFD&\3c&H3F37AC&\4c&H3F37AC&\pos(673,270)\shad2}中\N獎\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學 走廊裡不要跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 可讓我好找啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧！ 疼不疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是你想像的那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說那些事了 今天可以去名乃家麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是驚喜我不能跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就回頭見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就連相生同學們那份也買了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭 接下來是布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許耍賴喲 石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個南瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真硬！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 死小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大將嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中… 中村！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找你好久了哦 大將！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧你沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記我了嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為沒忘才要跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將 吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大將？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H929893&\frz22.932\pos(180,211)}機器人研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\frz16.372\pos(659,145)\c&H595E52&}和貓生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話就要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將 那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來啊 大將！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 中村老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東雲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 做點什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在找些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛機器人撲火就是在說她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7}飛んで火にいる夏のロボット：{\r\fs33}原本該是{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}飛んで火にいる夏の虫{\r\fs33}，指飛蛾撲火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在學校總能和東雲見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優先找大將！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 東雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到一隻黑貓麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中村老師家裡養了一隻黑貓麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算… 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心讓它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們家也有一隻黑貓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟著一起找找可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦 東雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 中村老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師的貓叫什麼名字啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家的貓叫阪本先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是奇怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大將 可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你這是在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 中村倒也不是故意那麼做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總被那樣的傻事整的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,470)\shad0\bord0\c&H39213E&\pos(842,574)}關於總做傻事的中村的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也沒什麼大改變嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H39213E&\pos(402,574)}關於總是惡作劇的小鬼的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天平 紋絲不動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 中村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不新鮮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了的話 我可以去看看大將麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！ 隨時歡迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管去哪邊都是最糟糕啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 阪本先生 我回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了嗎 博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又被阪本踩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取下來 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻再做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這麼簡單就能拿下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我自己想取下來可完全夠不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃自己取不下來但別人可以取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 插進去的話名乃自己也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼機能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個「小東西」有什麼機能啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個取下來的話拇指就不能飛出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊 那種機能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是相生同學她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小祐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小祐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發條得收好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我看起來也像普通人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會比之前跟大家關係更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起去哪裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更加普通又快樂的日常可能在等著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說那些事了 今天可以去名乃家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為可愛嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃就是名乃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就可以了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是來跟你說這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都差點忘記了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓 安靜點！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的關頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們買來了一個蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是驚喜哦 驚喜～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 你太急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎 怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算神馬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}再來一次 再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼大家知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H362EE6&\frz335.465\pos(712,286)}名乃的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做好小東西了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個發條確實有好多不便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非～常想拿下來來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這樣挺好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是名乃高興的時候發條就會轉的「小東西」！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 可以幫我把這個蛋糕拿過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是蛋糕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把茶端過去所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們兩個在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相生同學 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 抹布抹布！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡插上蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾！ 博士也要來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 比起那個 怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要整理乾淨啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抹布 抹布！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀都說了 要整理乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻衣 STOP STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:58.35,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白い光の中に　山並みは萌えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:58.35,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}潔白的光芒中  群山又長出新綠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:08.70,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}はるかな空の果てまでも　君は飛び立つ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:08.70,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}就算遙遠的天空的盡頭  你也能飛過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:19.71,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}限りなく青い空に　心ふるわせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:19.71,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}無邊的湛藍的天空  震顫著心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:30.06,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}自由をかける鳥よ　振り返ることもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:30.06,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}自由翱翔的鳥兒啊  頭也不回的向前飛去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:40.39,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}勇気を翼に込めて　希望の風に乗り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:40.39,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}將勇氣裝在翅膀上  乘著那希望之風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:52.31,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\blur3}この広い大空に　夢を託して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:52.31,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\blur3}向這廣闊的天空  托付夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:06.12,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\shad2\pos(1100,360)\4c&HE8DAD9&}幹\N勁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噴嚏打個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噴嚏什麼的靠氣勢就能止住哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 止住有氣勢之前的噴嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之一定要停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒可能沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個單純的笨蛋
